mentary interior design service to its clients and sells a range of furniture products and decorative accents through ethanallencom and a network of design centers in the united states and abroad its wholesale segment principally involved in the development of the ethan allen brand encompasses various aspects of design manufacture sourcing sale and distribution of its range of home furnishings and accents the companys retail segment sells home furnishings and accents to consumers through a network of companyoperated design centers as of june   the company owned and operated nine manufacturing facilities more from reuters » officers and directors m farooq kathwari chairman of the board president chief executive officer age  bio  compensation   reuters trading activity  yahoo finance corey whitely chief financial officer executive vice president  administration treasurer age  bio  compensation   reuters trading activity  yahoo finance daniel m grow senior vice president  business development age  bio  compensation   reuters eric d koster vice president general counsel secretary age  bio  compensation   reuters john s bedford vice president corporate controller age  bio  compensation   reuters tracy paccione vice president  merchandising age  bio  compensation   reuters clifford thorn vice president  upholstery manufacturing age  bio  compensation   reuters john j dooner jr lead independent director age  bio  compensation   reuters james b carlson independent director age  bio  compensation   reuters domenick j esposito independent director age  bio  compensation   reuters full list on reuters » google finance beta available in hong kong  canada  us  china  ukinformation is provided as is and solely for informational purposes not for trading purposes or advice and may be delayedto see all exchange delays please see disclaimer google  google home  blog  help  report a problem  privacy policy  terms of service shop dining rooms  ethan allen your browsers javascript funct