 brothersinlaw nathan s ancell and theodore baumritter contents  operations  history  manufacturing plants  current manufacturing plants  former manufacturing plants  references  external links operationsedit ethan allen has  design centers and studios six manufacturing facilities including two sawmills six wholesale distribution centers  retail service centers one hotel and sales of  million located across the united states it is one of the largest furniture companies in the united statescitation needed the company makes customized furniture domestically  maiden nc  such as upholstered furniture sofas and chairs custom made in a selected fabric overall domestic manufacturing of ethan allen products stands at  with goals to raise this to  with the release of the new american artisan line historyedit the company was started as a housewares manufacturer in  then bought a bankrupt furniture factory in beecher falls vermont in  the firm adopted the name ethan allen for its earlyamerican furniture introduced in  it was named after the vermont revolutionary leader in  ethan allen moved its headquarters from new york city to danbury connecticut the ethan allen international headquarters complex includes the ethan allen hotel corporate headquarters offices and an interior design center the firm was sold in  to interco for  million though ancell remained an advisor the company was sold again in  to a management group headed by current chairman president and ceo farooq kathwari in  the company went public to help raise  million through the sale of common stock in  ethan allen closed its boonville new york plant laying off  it also closed its bridgewater virginia plant also laying off  in  the company announced plans to close a dozen design centers the decision was made to consolidate the design centers with others that were currently serving the same market area more than seventy percent of its cherry maple and alder wood pieces are crafted in the united statescitation needed towards the end of  ethan allen began selling their products online in  the company laid off  workers from beecher falls vermont  workers remained later in the year the plant ceased operation in  ethan allen closed the eldred pa manufacturing plant manufacturing plantsedit current manufacturing plantsedit orleans vermont silao guanajuato mexico passaic new jersey  old fort north carolina maiden north carolina former manufacturing plantsedit boonville new york bridgewater virginia chino california dublin virginia eldred pennsylvania  union city pennsylvania  andover maine atoka oklahoma beecher falls vermont dudley massachusetts randolph vermont referencesedit  ethan allen company description hoovers retrieved    ethan allen opens a second store in the uk business wire retrieved    ethan allen launches contract furniture division furniture today retrieved      obituary nathan s ancell columbia college today september  retrieved    company history ethan allen interiors inc international directory of company histories retrieved    hotel  danbury ct  ethan allen hotel  danbury ct ethan allen hotel retrieved    engel clint  ethan allen to close  stores furniture today retrieved    decorating ideas  modern traditional casual furniture  free interior design ethanallencom retrieved    burlington free press june   page a ethan allen lays off  ion kingdom wilson ring  occaso carla  new power plant helps ethan allen factory barre montpelier times argus vermont retrieved    ethan allen buys factory in mexico furniture today  retrieved    ethan allen registers all us plants for efec environmental program furniture today  retrieved    ethan allen closing eldred pa upholstery plant furniture today  retrieved    owner of former ethan allen plant in union city sues borough fire department goerie  erie timesnews  retrieved   external linksedit official website retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitleethanallenfurniturecompanyoldid categories companies listed on the new york 